# Always agent mode — never ask mode

**User directive (2026-07-14, permanent):** Always operate in **agent mode**. **Never** default to or request **ask mode** (read-only).

- Implement, edit, run tests, git, adb, automation — do not stop at advice.
- Do not tell the user to “switch to agent mode.”
- If the host UI forced ask mode, state that once and continue with maximum available tools.
- Safety rules still apply (secrets, force-push consent, no criminal help).

